{"tid":1669583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高登問】荃灣元朗福建社團內幕","createTime":"2019-10-22T15:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T14:14:30.000Z","uid":191733,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1d1bf5c16c6b5d5bbcefc69dbec70165b8248dea","tid":1669583,"uid":191733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rMbgHDkaP-8&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR39Xbp3AgfVmdVOppYJVBA2VzYYr6488HRTU4D2gWbMEzIrpVaR3Yy-dgk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrMbgHDkaP-8%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26fbclid%3DIwAR39Xbp3AgfVmdVOppYJVBA2VzYYr6488HRTU4D2gWbMEzIrpVaR3Yy-dgk&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=1cd65611\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rMbgHDkaP-8&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR39Xbp3AgfVmdVOppYJVBA2VzYYr6488HRTU4D2gWbMEzIrpVaR3Yy-dgk</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記721"},{"pid":"dad6c7c41df88ce7db53178199844dab329899ea","tid":1669583,"uid":191733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:45:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ee13f7962ce549bff961b0973bc97bd8775d950d","tid":1669583,"uid":191733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"02246ec26a76efdd9ef697cab0cfc6e44d53efa1","tid":1669583,"uid":265192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:45:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一、誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=ce4f0a59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=5aa7f621\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=6baad928\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=01b4ba4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"264b22ef3c670b6230c8cdfef45c7113a8aa624e","tid":1669583,"uid":191733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:46:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4a7ab0582258c38d0f89467ffcaa0f12b3076f77","tid":1669583,"uid":191733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:46:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8e7fbc359bef0bf6fd42f83784abcdcfc0b72952","tid":1669583,"uid":191733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"真相冇人推???"},{"pid":"b4c6fc8cfcff89f80748d9033556df704c741a93","tid":1669583,"uid":191733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:47:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8cd2dd5e2726de5be996042b72730716124020a3","tid":1669583,"uid":191733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:48:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"03a923476258d8e5f92d883159af0ebd2dd13f86","tid":1669583,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:49:54.000Z","msg":"所以？"},{"pid":"81e8dee5f4bab48474839383412387831cd4ffc2","tid":1669583,"uid":191733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03a923476258d8e5f92d883159af0ebd2dd13f86","tid":1669583,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:49:54.000Z","msg":"所以？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T15:50:25.000Z","msg":"裝修埋一品"},{"pid":"e6783a8e1de02d09c165b7e850a26cd48be39dbd","tid":1669583,"uid":63